parts.text: what tools do you have and what you can do

I have tools to interact with Notion. I can:

*   **Search**: Search for pages and databases by title.
*   **Pages**:
    *   Retrieve a page's content and properties.
    *   Create a new page.
    *   Update a page's properties.
*   **Blocks**:
    *   Retrieve a block's content.
    *   Append new blocks as children to an existing block (or page).
    *   Update a block's content (text and to-do checked status).
    *   Delete/archive a block.
*   **Databases**:
    *   Query a database to retrieve pages based on filters and sorts.
    *   Retrieve a database's schema and properties.
    *   Create a new database.
    *   Update a database's title or description.
*   **Comments**:
    *   Retrieve comments on a block or page.
    *   Create new comments on a page.
*   **Users**:
    *   Retrieve a specific user.
    *   List all users in the workspace.
    *   Retrieve information about the bot user associated with the integration.
*   **Page Properties**:
    *   Retrieve a specific property item from a page.

In short, I can help you read, write, and manage content within your Notion workspace!

parts.text: tell me what is given in these page - Poetry / Shayari (ID: 1d285596-7db8-809f-b512-f3da0f0a0ec4)

Here's the content of the "Poetry / Shayari" page:

Jhuto ke beech mei mai sach bol betha wah namak ka saher tha aur mai apne sakhm khol betha 

Fasle ese bhi honge socha na tha 
Samne batha tha wah mera ,par wah mera na tha.

Kabhi mil to tujhe bataya hum ,tujhe iss tarah sataye hum,tera ishq tujhe chin kar,
Tujhe meh pila kar rulaye hum .
Tujhe dard du,tu na seh sake.
Tujhe du zuban tu na keh sake.
Tujhe du makkan tu na reh sake .
Tujhe mushkilo mai geera kar mai koi esa rasta nikal du kee tere dard ki mai dua banu.

Chandi Sina ek taraf ,tera hona ek taraf .
Ek taraf hai teri aankhein , Jaadu tona ek taraf 

Mohaabat inshan ko bahut kamzor bana deti hai .Kabhi kisi se mohabbat na karna 
Kha ma kha sari zindagi apne he nazro mai sharminda hote rahoge.

Ek alladh sa ladka tha mai jin dino ek mele mai nikala humkta hua je machalata tha ek ek cheez pr magar,par mol na de saka kisi cheez ka.aaj mela laga hai ussi shaan se,aaj chahu to ek ek dukaan mol lu,aaj chahu to sara chaa mol lu.par abb jee mei rasayi ka dhadka kaha,au abb mai wah chota sa alladh sa ladka kaha
Ek allhad sa ladka tha main...
Jin dino ek mele se guzarta tha,
Muskaan thi aankhon mein,
Jee machlata tha har cheez par...
Par mol... kabhi na de saka.
Aaj bhi mela laga hai,
Ussi roshni, ussi rangin shaan ke saath.
Aaj chahoon toh...
Ek-ek dukaan kharid loon,
Chaand bhi, apni jeb mein bhar loon...
Lekin...
Ab jee mein woh dhadkan kahan?
Woh ras bhari, beparwah si chahat kahan?
Aur main bhi...
Ab woh chhota sa allhad sa ladka...
Kahan?

Yea zid hai hamari ke tumhe chin lein sbse
Gamon aur zamane se takaja nahi karte wo ro lete hai gosaye tanhai mai aksar hum saher ke gaaliyon mai tamasha nahi karte

Yu bhi ho sakata hai ke ek pal Mai koi acha lag jaye ,baat koi bhi na ho aur dil mai tamasha ho jaye .

Mohaabat mai jo sun rakha tha waisa kuch nahi hota ke isme banda mar jata hai jyada kuch nahi hota ke filmo mai he sabko pyar mil jata hai akhir mai .magar sach much iss duniya mai esa kuch nahi hota .meri gurbat ne mujh se meri duniya chin Lee hafi.meri ammi to kehti thi ke paesa sab kuch nahi hota 

Hasrat hai ke usse jee bhar kar dekhu ,
Masla yeh bhi ke jee bharega kya

Wah shone ke kangan pahen chuki thi 
Jab mai chudiyaa kharidne ke kaabil hua

Kangan teri hatho mea pahena achaa lage 
Har dard tere ishq mae sahena acha lage 
Aate ho samne ban sawar ke jab bhi 
Har baar meri ankhon ko tujhe dekhana acha lage

parts.text: what tools do you have and what you can do

I have tools to interact with Notion. I can:

*   **Search**: Search for pages and databases by title.
*   **Pages**:
    *   Retrieve a page's content and properties.
    *   Create a new page.
    *   Update a page's properties.
*   **Blocks**:
    *   Retrieve a block's content.
    *   Append new blocks as children to an existing block (or page).
    *   Update a block's content (text and to-do checked status).
    *   Delete/archive a block.
*   **Databases**:
    *   Query a database to retrieve pages based on filters and sorts.
    *   Retrieve a database's schema and properties.
    *   Create a new database.
    *   Update a database's title or description.
*   **Comments**:
    *   Retrieve comments on a block or page.
    *   Create new comments on a page.
*   **Users**:
    *   Retrieve a specific user.
    *   List all users in the workspace.
    *   Retrieve information about the bot user associated with the integration.
*   **Page Properties**:
    *   Retrieve a specific property item from a page.

In short, I can help you read, write, and manage content within your Notion workspace!

*   Integrate API KEY.
*   Users do not need an API KEY for publicly available agents.
*   For private agents, users must request access from the provider.
*   A method should be used to store agent-cards to avoid unnecessary API calls to fetch agent IDs.
*   The next step is to work on the CLI tool.

parts.text: tell me what is given in these page - Poetry / Shayari (ID: 1d285596-7db8-809f-b512-f3da0f0a0ec4)

Here's the content of the "Poetry / Shayari" page:

Jhuto ke beech mei mai sach bol betha wah namak ka saher tha aur mai apne sakhm khol betha 

Fasle ese bhi honge socha na tha 
Samne batha tha wah mera ,par wah mera na tha.

Kabhi mil to tujhe bataya hum ,tujhe iss tarah sataye hum,tera ishq tujhe chin kar,
Tujhe meh pila kar rulaye hum .
Tujhe dard du,tu na seh sake.
Tujhe du zuban tu na keh sake.
Tujhe du makkan tu na reh sake .
Tujhe mushkilo mai geera kar mai koi esa rasta nikal du kee tere dard ki mai dua banu.

Chandi Sina ek taraf ,tera hona ek taraf .
Ek taraf hai teri aankhein , Jaadu tona ek taraf 

Mohaabat inshan ko bahut kamzor bana deti hai .Kabhi kisi se mohabbat na karna 
Kha ma kha sari zindagi apne he nazro mai sharminda hote rahoge.

Ek alladh sa ladka tha mai jin dino ek mele mai nikala humkta hua je machalata tha ek ek cheez pr magar,par mol na de saka kisi cheez ka.aaj mela laga hai ussi shaan se,aaj chahu to ek ek dukaan mol lu,aaj chahu to sara chaa mol lu.par abb jee mei rasayi ka dhadka kaha,au abb mai wah chota sa alladh sa ladka kaha
Ek allhad sa ladka tha main...
Jin dino ek mele se guzarta tha,
Muskaan thi aankhon mein,
Jee machlata tha har cheez par...
Par mol... kabhi na de saka.
Aaj bhi mela laga hai,
Ussi roshni, ussi rangin shaan ke saath.
Aaj chahoon toh...
Ek-ek dukaan kharid loon,
Chaand bhi, apni jeb mein bhar loon...
Lekin...
Ab jee mein woh dhadkan kahan?
Woh ras bhari, beparwah si chahat kahan?
Aur main bhi...
Ab woh chhota sa allhad sa ladka...
Kahan?

Yea zid hai hamari ke tumhe chin lein sbse
Gamon aur zamane se takaja nahi karte wo ro lete hai gosaye tanhai mai aksar hum saher ke gaaliyon mai tamasha nahi karte

Yu bhi ho sakata hai ke ek pal Mai koi acha lag jaye ,baat koi bhi na ho aur dil mai tamasha ho jaye .

Mohaabat mai jo sun rakha tha waisa kuch nahi hota ke isme banda mar jata hai jyada kuch nahi hota ke filmo mai he sabko pyar mil jata hai akhir mai .magar sach much iss duniya mai esa kuch nahi hota .meri gurbat ne mujh se meri duniya chin Lee hafi.meri ammi to kehti thi ke paesa sab kuch nahi hota 

Hasrat hai ke usse jee bhar kar dekhu ,
Masla yeh bhi ke jee bharega kya

Wah shone ke kangan pahen chuki thi 
Jab mai chudiyaa kharidne ke kaabil hua

Kangan teri hatho mea pahena achaa lage 
Har dard tere ishq mae sahena acha lage 
Aate ho samne ban sawar ke jab bhi 
Har baar meri ankhon ko tujhe dekhana acha lage
